  "detailed_description": "<h1>ADD TO WISHLIST</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487110/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.poster.avif?t=1728547409\" width=736 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487110/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.webm?t=1728547409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487110/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.mp4?t=1728547409\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your <strong>master</strong> was a very good <strong>alchemist</strong>, but it is time for you to become more than an <strong>apprentice</strong>. You have improved a lot and can create <strong>potions</strong> that even your master cannot make. Finding the Philosopher's Stone is your destiny; it's the only way to see your mother again. However, this journey won't be easy. Are you still here? Show them how good an alchemist you are!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect Materials</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Plants</strong>, <strong>mushrooms</strong>, <strong>minerals</strong> and <strong>animal parts</strong> are the basic ingredients for creating potions. Take on apprentices and leave them to the resources to gather ingredients. Make no mistake, they will get you the best ingredients. Don't forget to give them their gold at the end of the day!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487110/extras/69b57f09566120276f2dc2468f341c52.poster.avif?t=1728547409\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487110/extras/69b57f09566120276f2dc2468f341c52.webm?t=1728547409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Brew Potion</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you have the ingredients, you can make potions. Don't keep the customers waiting, get to work right away. Don't forget to use your tool cards while making potions, we'd like to see you as a master alchemist, wouldn't we?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487110/extras/e1cbb9891e092d0e4453c94c551bc14a.poster.avif?t=1728547409\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487110/extras/e1cbb9891e092d0e4453c94c551bc14a.webm?t=1728547409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sell Potions</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Well, you can't do business on an empty stomach. Let's make some money. You can earn <strong>gold</strong> by selling your potions to customers. Don't forget us if you get rich, okay?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487110/extras/e757667a07bd8bcb20d84d056e6bca99.poster.avif?t=1728547409\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487110/extras/e757667a07bd8bcb20d84d056e6bca99.webm?t=1728547409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Improve Your Shop</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now that you've got the money, why don't you upgrade your potion shop? You can upgrade all your tool cards and increase their production speed. Of course, if you want to produce <strong>The Philosopher's Stone</strong>, that's up to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487110/extras/dd2d8973611eb15ead2879596e41838a.poster.avif?t=1728547409\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487110/extras/dd2d8973611eb15ead2879596e41838a.webm?t=1728547409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Attention Attention!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not everything is so easy, of course there are challenges. Be careful not to be harmed by <strong>bandits</strong> or <strong>wild animals</strong>. You can train your apprentices and overcome enemy cards. You can do it, right?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487110/extras/2536cfd0e097a8c2a4ec6d7709e3d8b4.poster.avif?t=1728547409\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487110/extras/2536cfd0e097a8c2a4ec6d7709e3d8b4.webm?t=1728547409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features: </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>+3000</strong> Unique Potion</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>+200</strong> Unique Card</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Card Transformations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combat System</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your <strong>master</strong> was a very good <strong>alchemist</strong>, but it is time for you to become more than an <strong>apprentice</strong>. You have improved a lot and can create <strong>potions</strong> that even your master cannot make. Finding the Philosopher's Stone is your destiny; it's the only way to see your mother again. However, this journey won't be easy. Are you still here? Show them how good an alchemist you are!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect Materials</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Plants</strong>, <strong>mushrooms</strong>, <strong>minerals</strong> and <strong>animal parts</strong> are the basic ingredients for creating potions. Take on apprentices and leave them to the resources to gather ingredients. Make no mistake, they will get you the best ingredients. Don't forget to give them their gold at the end of the day!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487110/extras/69b57f09566120276f2dc2468f341c52.poster.avif?t=1728547409\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487110/extras/69b57f09566120276f2dc2468f341c52.webm?t=1728547409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Brew Potion</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you have the ingredients, you can make potions. Don't keep the customers waiting, get to work right away. Don't forget to use your tool cards while making potions, we'd like to see you as a master alchemist, wouldn't we?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487110/extras/e1cbb9891e092d0e4453c94c551bc14a.poster.avif?t=1728547409\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487110/extras/e1cbb9891e092d0e4453c94c551bc14a.webm?t=1728547409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sell Potions</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Well, you can't do business on an empty stomach. Let's make some money. You can earn <strong>gold</strong> by selling your potions to customers. Don't forget us if you get rich, okay?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487110/extras/e757667a07bd8bcb20d84d056e6bca99.poster.avif?t=1728547409\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487110/extras/e757667a07bd8bcb20d84d056e6bca99.webm?t=1728547409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Improve Your Shop</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now that you've got the money, why don't you upgrade your potion shop? You can upgrade all your tool cards and increase their production speed. Of course, if you want to produce <strong>The Philosopher's Stone</strong>, that's up to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487110/extras/dd2d8973611eb15ead2879596e41838a.poster.avif?t=1728547409\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2487110/extras/dd2d8973611eb15ead2879596e41838a.webm?t=1728547409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs